app.entity_classes

Class SalesItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.entity_classes.SalesItems

  • public class SalesItems
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an item within a sales transaction.

    This class encapsulates the details of a sales item, including its own ID, the ID of the sale it belongs to, and the ID of the item being sold.
